Introduction

Rumble-G was a South Korean girl group under WinnerZone Entertainment, consisting of two members: Didi and Barum.They debuted on July 14, 2021 with Roopretelcham. Ian‘s departure from the group was announced on November 19th, 2021. Gayun’s departure was announced on November 7, 2022.

They are presumed to have disbanded due to a lack of social media activity since 2023.
